# Frontend rules

Applies to `src/**/*.{ts,tsx,css,html}` and any root HTML/CSS that becomes part of the frontend build.

## Implementation guidance

- Prefer small, focused components under `src/components/`.
- Avoid hard dependencies on Webflow runtime (`webflow.js`) in new code.
- Keep assets under `public/` and reference them via stable paths.
- In the Worker-served site, avoid client-side routing unless explicitly implemented later.
